$interpreted: Yao: Mngh... how long was I asleep?
Yao: (I remember after I dealt with the Bloodfangs, I came here to tend to my wounds...)
Yao: ...One more thing.
Citizen: Did you hear about that little village in the valley? Everyone was massacred.
Merchant: No way... Do you think it was that wandering murderer?
Bloodfang Officer: I'm sorry, I was wrong! Please let me go!!
Joo-Won: You're here.
Yao: I caught a whiff of blood.
Joo-Won: I forget how familiar you must be with this horrid smell...
Yao: ……
Joo-Won: Do you know what they did to my wife and friends?
Joo-Won: I thought if I could avenge them, things might be better... Then those killers found me, and I slaughtered them all.
Joo-Won: One, two, three... I killed so many men.
Joo-Won: And yet that god-forsaken backstabber wasn't anywhere to be found! She hid! She ran away like a coward!
Joo-Won: I suppose that's what you wanted me to see... the evil in human nature... You knew this might happen!
Yao: Yes, but I don't care.
Joo-Won: That's right, you've never cared. You're a criminal... and now I am, too.
Joo-Won: Gyaagh!!
Yao: One day, you'll realize your beliefs are hollow. Such a farce, you'll want to laugh but won't have the strength.
Yao: And then you'll realize, you're a criminal, too.
Joo-Won: Is that so...? Then I suppose you don't understand where my belief comes from.
Joo-Won: And yet, if that day truly comes, where I fall from grace... I beg you stop me in my tracks.
Joo-Won: Night Wanderer... Thank you...
Yao: This place used to be so filled with hope...
Yao: And yet this world wasn't strong enough for that hope, so it shattered and fell away, piece by piece...
Yao: He asked me, if I wasn't fighting for justice, then what was I fighting for?
Yao: But what he didn't understand was,
Yao: I am fighting for justice.
Yao: Revenge is justice!!
Bloodfang Leader: Faster!! We still have a lot of work to do, here!
Lackey: Yes, boss!
Bloodfang Leader: Bwahaha~ Good thing I used to be in charge of all the Bloodfangs' correspondence... now I can take all their clients!
Bloodfang Leader: What luck~
Yao: I agree.
Bloodfang Leader: Eh!? Who's there!?
Yao: Your reckoning.
